original: Järneström, Erik Kristoffer, advokat, Västervik, f. 13/10/18 i Härnö-•sand av adv. P. J. o. Hedvig Nordlander. G. 44" m. Inez Hansson. Barn: Anita f. 46. — Stud:ex. 36, jur. kand. 41. Not. v. Aska, Dals o. Bobergs doms. o. v. Sthlms rådhusr. 41-43, in-neh. av W. Örnös Adv :byrå i Västervik sed. 44. Suppl. i styr. f. Sv. Handibankens kont. i Västervik sed. 46. Hobby: tennis.
translated: Järneström, Erik Kristoffer, lawyer, from Västervik, born on October 13, 1918 in Härnösand to lawyer P.J. and Hedvig Nordlander. Married in 1944 to Inez Hansson with a daughter named Anita, born in 1946. Graduated from high school in 1936 and received his degree in law in 1941. Became a notary in Aska, Dals, Boberg's courts, and Stockholm City Court from 1941 to 1943. Established his own law firm at W. Örnös in Västervik in 1944. Appointed as a representative to the board of the Swedish Handelsbanken's office in Västervik since 1946. Enjoys tennis as a hobby.
